<title>CSS 2.1 Test Suite: Test for z-ordering of inline-table</title>
<link href="https://dbaron.org/" rel="author" title="L. David Baron" />
<link href="http://mozilla.com/" rel="author" title="Mozilla Corporation" />
<link href="http://www.w3.org/TR/CSS21/zindex.html#painting-order" rel="help" />
